extDesc.message: Optimized fuzzy omnibox history search - Like firefox quick history search.

omniboxDefault.message: Use CTRL+SHIFT+0 to open quick history search without the omnibox

help_2.message:
Most visited entries are on top. Type in what you know from an url, seperate multiple words by space to specify the search even more.
Example: %s find all urls that contains %s and %s.

help_4.message: DEL Key will remove the current highlighted entry from your history
